== OLLMchat API - Package Overview ==

This documentation covers the OLLMchat application and its libraries. The codebase is split into several namespaces; below are the main ones with short descriptions and links.

== Core libraries (no GTK) ==

* ''{@link OLLMfiles}'' — File and project management: buffers, files, folders, project list, tree-sitter AST paths, diff/patch. Use when you need file access, project roots, or code structure without GUI.

* ''{@link OLLMchat}'' — LLM chat client: Ollama/OpenAI-compatible API, ''{@link OLLMchat.Call}'' and ''{@link OLLMchat.Response}'' operations, ''{@link OLLMchat.Tool}'' (function calling), ''{@link OLLMchat.History}'', ''{@link OLLMchat.Settings}'', ''{@link OLLMchat.Agent}''. Use for all chat, tools, and agent logic outside the UI.

* ''{@link OLLMvector}'' — Vector search and codebase indexing: embeddings, FAISS, ''{@link OLLMvector.Indexing}'' pipeline (tree-sitter, analysis, vector build), ''{@link OLLMvector.Search}''. Use for semantic code/search and documentation indexing.

* ''{@link OLLMcoder}'' — Code-editor and task/skill layer: ''{@link OLLMcoder.Skill}'' (Runner, Manager, templates), ''{@link OLLMcoder.Task}'' (List, Details, Tool, Step). Use for skill-based task creation, refinement, and execution in the coding agent.

* ''OLLMtools'' (liboctools) — Built-in tools: ReadFile, WriteFile, RunCommand, WebFetch, GoogleSearch, Child agent. Registered via ''{@link OLLMchat.Tool}'' and used by the chat/agent stack.

== GTK / UI ==

* ''libocmarkdown'' — Markdown parsing and document model (no namespace in docs; see Parser, document/*, RenderBase). Used by skills and chat rendering.

* ''libocmarkdowngtk'' — GTK markdown rendering for the chat UI.

* ''libollmchatgtk'' — Chat widget, history browser, tool permission UI, model usage list. Application-facing GTK pieces.

* ''{@link OLLMapp}'' — Main application (Application, Window, settings dialogs). Entry point and window management.

== Low-level ==

* ''libocsqlite'' — SQLite wrapper (Database, Query, Schema). Used by libocfiles and libocvector.

== Quick links ==

  * ''{@link OLLMchat.Agent}'' — Agent interface and implementations (Base, JustAsk, Factory).
  * ''{@link OLLMcoder.Skill.Runner}'' — Runs the skill pipeline (task creation, refinement, execution).
  * ''{@link OLLMcoder.Task.List}'' — Task list and iteration.
  * ''{@link OLLMvector.Indexing.Indexer}'' — Code and documentation indexing entry point.
  * ''{@link OLLMvector.Search.Search}'' — Semantic codebase search.
